{"tid":1567411,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【果燃台3pm LIVE】藍絲號召去淘大唱國歌 傳逾百黑社會將到場製「7.21元朗恐襲2.0」","createTime":"2019-09-14T05:21:57.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T07:52:31.000Z","uid":75778,"like":89,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":71,"replies":[{"pid":"d854eb89cfbf8f1467fba7991eced1de12d1304b","tid":1567411,"uid":75778,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:21:57.000Z","msg":"淘大商場街坊日前（11日）聚集齊唱《願榮光歸香港》，有中年男子帶同3名年幼子女到場，突然唱國歌和近攝他人容貌，挑釁和指罵街坊，不但令其子女受驚，更與人爭執打鬥受傷。該涉事男子被網民發現為東華三院王余家潔紀念小學李姓教師。一批藍絲號召今午3時到淘大商場聚集合唱國歌，但多次採訪反送中運動的英籍記者Richard Scotford在facebook貼出一張對話截圖，對方引述一個「可信消息」指有逾百名香港及澳門黑社會成員今午3時將到淘大商場集合唱國歌，但實際目的是製造「7.21元朗恐襲2.0」，意指將會發生再度無差別襲擊市民的事件，叮囑Richard要小心。《蘋果》屆時將直播淘大情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n手足小心<br />\n有可能係局<br />\n黑社會打人<br />\n手足幫拖<br />\n黑警圍捕<br />\n完美劇本"},{"pid":"e70da9adb59e37d6776d8e907ee19c5076032e55","tid":1567411,"uid":234159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:24:20.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">各位手足聽日見！</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/good.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sixL0H5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsixL0H5.jpg&h=7456f0ec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Cis8d25.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCis8d25.jpg&h=359b5e5e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0af97d0732779e8fabeb650e6c5d93920e4383cc","tid":1567411,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:31:44.000Z","msg":"推，有無淘大撚"},{"pid":"690a2fc7e8cd043b98a40e35b4422e93ad0c8acb","tid":1567411,"uid":99461,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-14T05:35:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />流浮山 刀手到咗？"},{"pid":"1dd11437a3279f524e86080b012a06e78ca65651","tid":1567411,"uid":237733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,